                                    <div class="action">
                                        <p>Connect your camera to your local WiFi network by just pressing the <strong>WPS</strong> button (WiFi Protected Setup) and access your camera over the internet by scanning the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Network/Remote_Access/">P2P QR Code</a> with our <a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision/iPhone/P2P">iPhone</a>, <a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision/iPad/P2P">iPad</a>, <a href="/Software/Android/InstarVision/P2P">Android</a>, <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Windows_Phone/P2P">Windows Phone</a> and <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Metro/P2P">Windows (Metro)</a>.</p>
