                                <div class="action">
                                    <h4>Adjust your cameras focal point by simply turning the lense</h4>
                                    <p class="justify">Your camera will be adjusted to perform straight out of the box in general surveillance settings. For indoor surveillance this means that the lense is set to give you a sharp image of distance up to 5m. For special needs just <a href="/Indoor_Cameras/IN-8015_HD/Lense_Adjustment">turn the lense</a> and keep an eye on your live video - the lense can be adjusted for a near-focus down to a few centimeters or for a near infinity focus for tele-observations.</p>
