                                    <h4>Add a password to protect your privacy.</h4>
                                    <p class="justify">Please make sure to change the default username and password before forwarding your camera to the internet. Change the password for <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/System/User/">ll 3 user classes</a> - administrator, user and visitor - to make sure nobody is able to connect to your camera without your permission. You can use the cameras <a href="/Products/1080p/Camera_Reset">hardware reset</a>, in case you forgot your password.<br><br><br></p>
                                </div>
