                                      <h4>Motion Detection and Video Recording</h4>
                                      <p class="justify">Use your cameras internal image analysis in <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Actions/">combination with the integrated heat detector (PIR)</a> to efficiently detect people, animals or cars - while moving trees, passign clouds or automatically switched light sources are ignored. Set your camera to start a video or snapshot recording on the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Features/SD_Card/">local SD card</a> and upload those files to an off-site <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Network/FTP/">FTP server</a>.<br></p>
                                  </div>
