                                      <h4>Email and Push Notification</h4>
                                      <p class="justify">Set up your camera to detect motion to send you emails or push a notification to your smartphone. <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Push_Service/">Push notifications</a> (<a href="/Software/iOS/InstarVision">iOS</a>, <a href="/Software/Android/InstarVision">Android</a> and <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Windows_Phone">Windows Phone</a>) will reach you in an instance. While the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/Alarm/Actions/">email notification</a> might take a while, but added the bonus of attached snapshots. Activate both functions to be always informed about what is going on when you are on the road.<br><br></p>
